OL,5,
OL,6,CG2017FThe BBC News at Ten is struck
OL,7,Fdown by technical problems, when the
OL,8,Fprogramme's playout and graphics
OL,9,Fsystems crash moments before going on
OL,10,Fair.
OL,11,
OL,12,FThe programme is still put to air on
OL,13,Fthe BBC News channel and BBC One, with
OL,14,Fpresenter Huw Edwards left sitting at
OL,15,Fthe main presenting desk, in silence.
OL,16,
OL,17,FBBC One quickly switches to a programme
OL,18,Fmenu and then apology caption. Huw is
OL,19,Fleft on air on the BBC News channel for
OL,20,Fthe duration of the fault.
OL,21,
OL,22,FThe programme gets under way after 4
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
